.TH wnewmail "" "" "Command"
.PC "Asynchronously notify a user of new mail"
.fi
\fBwnewmail [\-d] [\-i \fIinterval\^\fB] \fImailbox \fB[\fImailbox ...\^\fB]\fR
.PP
The command
.B newmail
monitors mailboxes intelligently.
It is equivalent to the command
.BR "newmail \-w" .
For details on how to use this command, see the Lexicon entry for
.BR newmail .
.SH "See Also"
.B
commands,
elm,
mail (overview),
newmail
.R
